Key Match Events: France won 2-0 against Belgium with goals from Kolo Muani and Dembélé
Post-Match Reflections: National captain Kevin De Bruyne was highly critical of the team's performance, pointing to a lack of commitment from some team-mates
Miscellaneous Highlights: Belgium lost against France in the Nations League, despite a good opening phase
Others: Amadou Onana agreed with De Bruyne that motivation must never be lacking
